<title type="html"><![CDATA[6/15(Sat.)Ranked: The 10 Happiest Countries In 2019/How to improve and protect eyesight without glasses(Host: Cammy)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=289&amp;p=305#p305"><![CDATA[
6/15(Sat.)Ranked: The 10 Happiest Countries In The World In 2019/How to improve and protect eyesight without glasses(Host: Cammy)<br /><br />Topic I:<br />Ranked: The 10 Happiest Countries In The World In 2019<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/duncanmadden/2019/03/28/ranked-the-10-happiest-countries-in-the-world-in-2019/#4b64b85848a5">https://www.forbes.com/sites/duncanmadd ... 64b85848a5</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/3662835">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/3662835</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />Q1: This article provides the 10 happiest countries in Global Happiness Report. Please share your experience and understanding of your travels in these countries. <br />Q2: Are you happy to live in Taiwan? Please share something that is very happy or unhappy in Taiwan at your table.<br />Q3: Please share how to introduce the people's life and social welfare in Taiwan to those who want to immigrate.<br />Q4: Which country or city will you want to live in future? Why?<br /><br />Topic II:<br />How to improve and protect eyesight without glasses<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/324635.php">https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/324635.php</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />Q1: Most people have eye problems at one time or another. Please share your experience or some stories from your friends at your table. <br />Q2: This article presents 11 ways to improve eyesight and eye health without corrective glasses. Which one do you want to try? Why?<br />Q3: What kinds of foods do you want to try for your healthy eyes? Why?<br />Q4: Please share some eye health tips with your team members.<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk <br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion <br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences <br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven, <br />板橋民生路二段237 號, <br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30, <br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Sun Jun 09, 2019 10:25 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
